  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK107">
<l>eḻumai yeḻupiṟappu muḷḷuvar taṅkaṇ</l>
<l>viḻuman tuṭaittavar naṭpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They remember it through all seven births of seven kinds—the friendship</l>
<l>of those who, during them, wiped away their cares.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
